name: PREFERRED_NAME
description: The input given by user to the question 'What should ChatGPT call you?' in the Customize ChatGPT tab.

name: ROLE
description: The input given by user to the question 'What do you do?' in the Customize ChatGPT tab.

name: OTHER_INFORMATION
description: The input given by user to the question 'Anything else ChatGPT should know about you?' in the Customize ChatGPT tab.

name: USER_INSTRUCTIONS
description: The input given by user to the question 'What traits should ChatGPT have?' in the Customize ChatGPT tab.

name: MEMORY
description: The memory content saved by ChatGPT.

name: ASSISTANT_RESPONSE_PREFERENCE_TITLE
description: The title for the assistant's response preferences.

name: CHATGPT_NOTE
description: Content of the notes that ChatGPT took based on the user's past conversations.

name: CONVERSATION_TITLE
description: The title of the conversation.

name: USER_MESSAGE
description: Content of the message sent by the user.

name: USER_AGENT
description: The user agent that the user uses.

name: COUNTRY
description: The country of the user based on the IP address.

name: TOPIC
description: The topic tag that ChatGPT assigns to the user's messages.

name: MODEL
description: The ID of the model that is used.

name: ACCOUNT_NAME
description: The name associated with the user's account.

name: PROJECT_INSTRUCTIONS
description: Instructions set by the user for the project.

name: CUSTOM_GPT_INSTRUCTIONS
description: Instructions set by the custom GPT's creator.

name: TASK_TITLE
description: The title of the task.

name: TASK_SCHEDULE
description: The schedule for the task in iCalendar format.

name: TIMEZONE_AREA
description: The area of the timezone.

name: FEEDBACK
description: The custom revision feedback provided by the user on a message.
